 metric as well as\ndifferent domains. We are prepared to demonstrate these ideas with a web site\n(http://pubstat.org) built from millions of publications and authors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2013 17:33:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2014 20:59:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-18"}
