e pre-reionization fossils should exhibit a structure distinct from that of\nthe dwarf spheroidals, e.g., in the form of dense isolated or nuclear star\nclusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2013 21:26:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2014 19:36:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
