rties of\nthe inner and outer galaxy populations, testifying how the environment is\naffecting the galaxies. Instead, in NG groups there is no segregation between\nthe properties of galaxies in the inner and outer regions, showing that the\nproperties of these galaxies still reflect the physical processes prevailing in\nthe environment where they were found earlier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2013 00:22:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2013 13:27:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
